## ğŸ¨ Usage Examples

### Creating a React Project

```bash
$ devforge init --react
ğŸ§± Project name: my-awesome-app
Use TypeScript? (y/n) [y]: y
Enter features (comma separated) [core]: auth,profile,dashboard

âš™ï¸  Creating Vite project...
âœ… React project 'my-awesome-app' forged successfully!

ğŸ“¦ Next steps:
   cd my-awesome-app
   npm install
   npm run dev
```

### Creating a FastAPI Project

```bash
$ devforge init --fastapi
ğŸ§± Project name: my-api
Enter features (comma separated) [core]: auth,users,posts

âœ… FastAPI project 'my-api' forged successfully!

ğŸ“¦ Next steps:
   cd my-api
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

### Creating a Flutter Project

```bash
$ devforge init --flutter
ğŸ§± Project name: my_flutter_app
